	<h1 class="title">在电影和互联网都如此发达的美国，为什么大家不在网上买电影票？</h1>
	<div class="author-date clearfix">					
			<div class="author clearfix">
					<span class="avatar x25 circle">
						<img src="/system/users/faces/130051/small/130051.jpg?1435571000" alt="">
					</span>
				<span class="name">温欣语 </span>
			</div>
		<span class="date smart-date" data-originDate="2015-12-28 11:30:59 +0800"></span>
	</div>
	<div class="banner">
			<img src="/system/articles/articleshows/19496/medium/19496.jpg?1450754123" alt="" />			
	</div>
	<!-- 传入参数：obj(aritcle, paper, card, mob) -->


<div class="com-share" data-id="19496" data-title="《在电影和互联网都如此发达的美国，为什么大家不在网上买电影票？》，来自@好奇心日报" data-pic="http://www.qdaily.com/system/articles/articleshows/19496/medium/19496.jpg?1450754123" data-url="http://www.qdaily.com/mobile/articles/19496.html?from=singlemessage&amp;isappinstalled=1" data-weiboAppkey="2462590045">
